{"tid":633867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港教育局係咪李登輝同陳水扁嘅傳人？","createTime":"2018-04-18T16:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T16:45:20.000Z","uid":109462,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b22dc3813e6134c430674f8a93f5b2e84eeaf0b","tid":633867,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"執教科書字粒呢招其實當年李登輝已經用過，1997年李登輝先出一本《認識台灣》，將「日據時代」改做「日治時代」；十年後陳水扁委託台灣歷史學會做咗個《海洋教育與教科書用詞檢核計劃報告書》，列出大約5000個「不當用詞」要啲教科書改；又十年後輪到香港教育局搞鳩啲歷史教科書，乜都話你「用詞不當」。<br />\n<br />\n其實香港教育局係咪李登輝同陳水扁嘅傳人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/002016_51cf8d833c828a11f4592b83b86cfc71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F002016_51cf8d833c828a11f4592b83b86cfc71.png&h=8fa058e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/002024_4fdc927ef598d2cd3e9c1e314c6a9299.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F002024_4fdc927ef598d2cd3e9c1e314c6a9299.png&h=e04349b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/002136_7c4e4cca62372d1186fe2de398f45c83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F002136_7c4e4cca62372d1186fe2de398f45c83.png&h=30102637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/002025_a809e56984bf464a16a26ef55f1a2a72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F002025_a809e56984bf464a16a26ef55f1a2a72.png&h=ad97976e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/002026_60541bd289ded9390f9b0f6bce323c55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F0